OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAreas of low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog will gradually lift to leave a
OL,7,Fmainly dry day with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine. However, thicker cloud will
OL,9,Faffect central, northern and western
OL,10,Fparts of Scotland giving patchy rain.
OL,11,FFeeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning cloudy and breezy
OL,14,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fovernight. Some rain, especially
OL,16,Ftowards the north and west. Clearer
OL,17,Felsewhere, with patchy frost and some
OL,18,Flow cloud and fog returning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
