OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FPatchy rain will move
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards across the UK. Some
OL,7,Fsunshine developing across southern
OL,8,FEngland after a locally foggy start.
OL,9,FBrighter, colder weather arriving in
OL,10,Fthe northwest, with some blustery
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
